---
title: BBQ Sauce Chicken Breasts with Loaded Potatoes and Green Salad
description: With a fresh green salad, smoky BBQ chicken and loaded cheesy, sour cream potatoes, this dinner is everything you could possibly want on one plate. The family is going to be very happy tonight!
